On site responding to Total suspended solids hihi / fault and washwater pump lockout CMU5 #W11360943
ROC called about TSS high @09:53 - arrived on site @11:30 - Flushed lines to TSS analyzer and cleaned analyzer housing - TSS reading 0.6 mg/L after cleaning.  Alarms cleared, and washwater pumps back to standby
