Reviewed MIT and daily filter performance on all trains - no issues and all passed - recorded readings in PWQ sheets
@12:06 - train #4 shutdown on hihi turbdity on startup - reviewed trends, turbidity is coming down - placed train to M-clean as it is scheduled.  If alarm comes in again, will leave train off until tomorrow
No further issues on site
